### 4. Database Migration

#### [NEW] [scripts/add-solana-wallet.sql](file:///C:/GOLive/scripts/add-solana-wallet.sql)
```sql
ALTER TABLE profiles ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS solana_wallet_address text;
```
This migration is ready. User must run in Supabase SQL editor.

