## Verification Plan

### Automated (Code Review)
- Confirm no wallet addresses in source code
- Confirm env vars used throughout

### Manual (On-Chain)
1. **Base Sepolia**: Deploy Splitter → send 0.001 ETH → verify 75/25 split on block explorer
2. **Solana Devnet**: Send 0.01 SOL → verify atomic split transaction on Solana Explorer
3. **USDC**: Test token transfer on both chains (Testnet)
